      },
      "date": "2020-04-20 08:05:14.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Sebastien\n > It looks like you abandoned your master equivalent to this patch.\n > Should we revert it from b2_12?\n\nhttps://review.whamcloud.com/38204 was abandoned because it was meant to be the patch for b2_12 but I pushed it on the wrong branch (bad 'git push' command on my side).\n\nThe equivalent on master of what is pushed here for b2_12 is https://review.whamcloud.com/37878. The master patch is much smaller because b2_12 still drags some remainders from the past (and this is the reason why the first port from master to b2_12 was incomplete).\n\nTo sum up, everything is fine, both in b2_12 and master :)",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
